article.description: — Joey Calcaterra posted 18 points and seven rebounds as San Diego got past Cal Poly 70-61 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Calcaterra carries San Diego past Cal Poly 70-61
article.linkText: Calcaterra carries San Diego past Cal Poly 70-61
article.story: SAN LUIS OBISPO, Calif. -- — Joey Calcaterra posted 18 points and seven rebounds as San Diego got past Cal Poly 70-61 on Wednesday. Frankie Hughes, the Toreros’ leading scorer entering the matchup at 16.0 points per game, made just 1 of 6 shots. Keith Smith had 12 points for the Mustangs (2-3). Hank Hollingsworth added 10 points and seven rebounds.
